description:
This is a 33 minute workout called 'Boost Recovery with Full Body Stretch Yoga for Athletes' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a Breathe and Flow yoga class for athletes to boost recovery. Also very suitable as a beginner yoga class. When resting you don't want to go crazy with your practice but still move the body a little. This class is ideal for that!
